創意產業研析（一）                       CREATIVE INDUSTRIES STUDIES （I）


  	本課程重點將培養研究生觀察、評估與思考創意生活在經濟與文化層次上的重要性，及如何營造創意生活的實踐方法，課程形式將透過教師引導，學生主導的方式讓學生勾勒創意生活的主要經濟與影響面向，進而深入透過實際體驗與接觸，尋找並探索創意生活的實質意義與內涵，課程內容將逐步透過:1)資料蒐集/接洽溝通，2)現場參與/互動觀摩，3)獨立分析與團體激盪，4)交叉評論與深度比較等四大階段與方式，針對創意生活各個面向進行實際接觸體驗與解析。(98)This course focuses on factors that contribute to creativity and innovation of individuals and groups within organizations in creative industry. In this ambitious course we will use experiential methods, case studies, workshops, and team projects, supported by guest speakers and readings.The goal of this course is to help students identify individual and organizational factors that promote and inhibit creative industries. We will explore a wide range of examples of creativity in individuals and organizations. In addition, students participate in long-term individual and team-based visiting projects designed to explore the variables that affect creativity and innovation. (98)

課程教育目標 

A 創意產業跨領域整合研究與人才 Research of interdisciplinary integration and talent incubator in creative industriesB 國際與華人創產研究之學術重鎮與產官學研智庫 The academic hub for international and Chinese in creatiD 創意產業本土理論論述與國際匯流 Theoretical discourse of local creative industries and international convergen 
課程基本素養與核心能力 

A 人文素養

B 公民素養

1 跨領域整合能力

3 科技應用與設計能力


